{"tid":255250,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"肯plan 旅行行程既男仔一定係好男仔！","createTime":"2017-05-23T18:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T16:01:45.000Z","uid":104260,"like":128,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"47727dd2ccb6dc7cc05b8fa50f3d3e61b92240ed","tid":255250,"uid":104260,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:52:34.000Z","msg":"頭盔先<br />\n隨意玩都有隨意玩既好處<br />\n<br />\n不過Plan 行程係件好浪費時間心血既事 <br />\n要夠細心 唔係是但塞個景點<br />\n要考慮嗰日天氣 有無車去 幾耐一班 嗰日會唔會多人<br />\n考慮景點之間係咪順路 會唔會無野食<br />\n叻啲既仲可以accommodate 到男女需要<br />\n唔會悶親大家<br />\n肯主動plan 行程 代表個男仔細心 有條理 負責任<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62a9c59f121aacc1fe2cd5bc7b0d720dcc66eee4","tid":255250,"uid":118357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:54:12.000Z","msg":"過幾日同男友去京阪<br />\n我同佢都係第一次去<br />\n然後得我一個plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c6bc53061c456359e42cf39e8f214d4242436a8","tid":255250,"uid":104260,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:54:33.000Z","msg":"你老味 我負責book 機票住宿<br />\n叫男朋友幫手plan行程 睇下有咩地方想去<br />\n佢話 得啦 你搞啦 我信得過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec2756d2c80c9b3ea1814d486c2402bec25ace0","tid":255250,"uid":118357,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老味 我負責book 機票住宿<br />\n叫男朋友幫手plan行程 睇下有咩地方想去<br />\n佢話 得啦 你搞啦 我信得過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同我男友一撚樣<br />\n問佢咩都話無所謂 你決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2525114523bc7b8079c2d21a7d97d5444ccb7bf","tid":255250,"uid":73369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T18:59:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你老味 我負責book 機票住宿<br />\n叫男朋友幫手plan行程 睇下有咩地方想去<br />\n佢話 得啦 你搞啦 我信得過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假如機票酒店都係男仔book的話<br />\n女仔plan返行程 <br />\n你地又會點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ea1a4d203a8e942959644d8ec0ad699f0c7145d","tid":255250,"uid":104260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:06:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你老味 我負責book 機票住宿<br />\n叫男朋友幫手plan行程 睇下有咩地方想去<br />\n佢話 得啦 你搞啦 我信得過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n假如機票酒店都係男仔book的話<br />\n女仔plan返行程 <br />\n你地又會點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n2個人一齊去 緊係2個人plan 啦<br />\n你無份玩既！ <br />\n仲有 我撚知你歡唔歡喜我嗰啲景點<br />\n一陣去到又西面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d852b6687a4a3c2200131c566b938f3ef432311","tid":255250,"uid":97814,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:09:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10d96ce951bb781d557fe59a07cf22bda15aa245","tid":255250,"uid":104260,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>床上餵飽你咪得 其他隨意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫你plan 個行程都唔撚得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚俾你屌啊！</span>"},{"pid":"bed3ab9a34211dafb331d9dfaedd3ca3b5ef0e54","tid":255250,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:12:41.000Z","msg":"因為同女朋友去旅行，<br />\n男既只係志在晚上既享樂，<br />\n其他野wfc？"},{"pid":"4b8766b9e8ad1dfa4428fa04176ff4722c460150","tid":255250,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:16:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cca74568c2aa5feb5ca5d02180886da08b631dd7","tid":255250,"uid":104260,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:16:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>床上餵飽你咪得 其他隨意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫你plan 個行程都唔撚得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚俾你屌啊！</span></blockquote><br />\n洗費男方出 砌下都唔畀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n機票住宿都係我比架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfba685e38cf0f29ab8fa921ef1b05d1c62787e8","tid":255250,"uid":107157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:19:58.000Z","msg":"自己plan撚晒 唔洗理人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自私精 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7557b6410c89a353f4012d0ca64f8856216ed7d4","tid":255250,"uid":97814,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T19:20:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"faf5d17f5448484bc1b93020e2a61d553354bd68","tid":255250,"uid":5218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:17:14.000Z","msg":"行程住宿通常都係女友爭住做，我負責 plan 交通同比錢。"},{"pid":"d76f2b299060331c0f6bc4e936a0162f6ff042d3","tid":255250,"uid":64345,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:24:01.000Z","msg":"講到尾又係錢。<br />\n<br />\n唔使港女出錢就得"},{"pid":"1d124903c8fba215199826e3f15f7945825c1df5","tid":255250,"uid":41454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"樓主都講得o岩 如果連落力plan都唔肯就真係唔得掂<br />\n不過調返轉頭我對於係咪真係要plan行程呢件事好有懷疑 有時係咪大家對一定要plan好行程呢樣野太大期望?<br />\n路上有少少野唔o岩心水就燥<br />\n交通住宿景點果啲都算啦<br />\n有冇野食 點行點走 事實上好多contingency<br />\n我覺得有時唔洗plan得咁死<br />\n所以自己一個旅行時我都唔太plan 隨心而行有時仲好<br />\n同人去就因為人地對我有期望所以就落力啲plan啦"},{"pid":"380a8a82331b25098def917c24692126450a7bcc","tid":255250,"uid":104260,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:39:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主都講得o岩 如果連落力plan都唔肯就真係唔得掂<br />\n不過調返轉頭我對於係咪真係要plan行程呢件事好有懷疑 有時係咪大家對一定要plan好行程呢樣野太大期望?<br />\n路上有少少野唔o岩心水就燥<br />\n交通住宿景點果啲都算啦<br />\n有冇野食 點行點走 事實上好多contingency<br />\n我覺得有時唔洗plan得咁死<br />\n所以自己一個旅行時我都唔太plan 隨心而行有時仲好<br />\n同人去就因為人地對我有期望所以就落力啲plan啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿 所以我都話隨心去無問題<br />\n但係你隨心都起碼知道大概有咩景點去係啦係咪先<br />\n<br />\n我男朋友係直程話<br />\n<br />\n唔理lu~~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ce1a154eef6ca1b6ffcd58a128e7ee9cf94e4a","tid":255250,"uid":78971,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:41:25.000Z","msg":"唔好成日攞呢啲肯xxxxxxxx就係好女朋友男朋友嚟打飛機或者幫另一半打飛機啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係咪好男女朋友平時自己感受唔到架咩<br />\n係要攞嚟講"},{"pid":"9231906010736889e3e3579b594d1a566c87f091","tid":255250,"uid":104138,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:42:17.000Z","msg":"以前我都有plan帶ex去富士山住左一晚睇日出,又遊左好多冷門地方<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但最後飛左後同左第2條仔一齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fe6936907b245a28cd93cbe3d4b8fbdec337eb","tid":255250,"uid":19004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:43:42.000Z","msg":"行唔行程唔重要<br />\n計下搭邊班車 時間幾耐個d 都要啦大佬<br />\n你估香港d 車去到咁夜咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2437255f477a66f42be59ae6d3d02d4ed66e50bb","tid":255250,"uid":41454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:44:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主都講得o岩 如果連落力plan都唔肯就真係唔得掂<br />\n不過調返轉頭我對於係咪真係要plan行程呢件事好有懷疑 有時係咪大家對一定要plan好行程呢樣野太大期望?<br />\n路上有少少野唔o岩心水就燥<br />\n交通住宿景點果啲都算啦<br />\n有冇野食 點行點走 事實上好多contingency<br />\n我覺得有時唔洗plan得咁死<br />\n所以自己一個旅行時我都唔太plan 隨心而行有時仲好<br />\n同人去就因為人地對我有期望所以就落力啲plan啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拿 所以我都話隨心去無問題<br />\n但係你隨心都起碼知道大概有咩景點去係啦係咪先<br />\n<br />\n我男朋友係直程話<br />\n<br />\n唔理lu~~~~~<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁我唔知佢咁係點諗啦<br />\n去旅行應該點都對個目的地有咩景點有個瞭解掛<br />\n唔係去黎做乜<br />\n借啲e扑嘢去澳門都得啦"},{"pid":"639286c118ceb21cc6496cbdb00ba75ddfccd2f9","tid":255250,"uid":65708,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T03:52:17.000Z","msg":"我覺得plan行程呢個過程好好玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果真係跟到哂或姐因爲突發事件用到後備plan都會有d成功感<br />\n上次旅行跟哂個plan最後竟然夠時間行多兩個景點"},{"pid":"bdaa3ce34cbfaf4d1892dc18b9519abd4dc78840","tid":255250,"uid":97878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:10:26.000Z","msg":"成班friend去得一個人plan<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"083d15e849154eb673ce6c46494fb002d797896a","tid":255250,"uid":41798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>床上餵飽你咪得 其他隨意</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n叫你plan 個行程都唔撚得<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚俾你屌啊！</span></blockquote><br />\n洗費男方出 砌下都唔畀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmo